videos.description: After Nate Reuvers drains a 3-pointer for Wisconsin, Devonte Green answers for Indiana with a 3 of his own.
videos.headline: Wisconsin, Indiana trade early 3s

videos.description: Rob Phinisee draws some attention and finds Devonte Green wide-open for an Indiana triple.

videos.description: Indiana's Rob Phinisee pokes the ball out and books it down the floor for the finger roll layup.
